gomodel:SYNGO_5281  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 4, 7: immunogold EM showed localization of P2X2 (gene P2RX2) to the side of the postsynaptic density of asymmetric synapses, at the plasma membrane, in sections from parallel fibers on Purkinje cells and CA1 stratum radiatum of the hippocampus.. Experimental description: rats were used for all assays.\nM&M: \"Western blot of brain homogenates. Brain homogenates were obtained from postnatal day 5 (P5) Sprague Dawley rats.\n...\nLight microscopic immunocytochemistry. Six P21 Sprague Dawley rats were anesthetized\"\n\nantibody:\n\"Antibodies to the C terminus of P2X2 and P2X4 were generated using a synthetic peptide corresponding to the following sequences: P2X2, DSTSTDPKGLAQL; P2X4, DYEQGLSGEMNQ.\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_5281" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

